          "front": "What are the treatments for Adenylosuccinase deficiency ?",
          "back": "How might adenylosuccinase deficiency be treated? At the current time, there are no effective therapies for the treatment of adenylosuccinase deficiency. Treatment is supportive based on the specific features."
